high_descs: Walk to the vanity on your right.
Pick up the green sponge on the counter next to the toilet.
Turn around and walk to the silver trash can in the corner.
Put the green sponge in the trash can.
Turn around and walk back to the vanity.
Pick up the green sponge on the counter between the two sinks.
Turn around and walk back to the trash can.
Put the green sponge in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two green sponges in the silver trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward to the basin.
Face down and pick up the sponge.
Turn around, move forward to the door, turn right, move forward to the bin and turn down.
Put the sponge in the bin.
Turn around, move forward to between the two basins on the left, turn left, move forward to the counter, face down.
Pick up the sponge.
Face up, turn around, move to the wall, turn right, move forward to the bin, turn down.
Put the sponge in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in the bathroom into the trash bin.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up sponge from the counter
Move to bin to the left of the toilet
Place sponge in the bin
Move to the counter in between the two sinks
Pick up sponge from the counter
Move to bin to the left of the toilet
Place sponge in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in the bin.
